### TeX ###
## Core latex/pdflatex auxiliary files:
*.aux
*.lof
*.log
*.lot
*.fls
*.out
*.toc

## Intermediate documents:
*.dvi
*-converted-to.*

### Editor ###
## Vim & Emacs temp files:
.*sw[op]
*~

### Mac OS X ###
## Mac OS X metadata files:
*.DS_Store

### Python ###
## Python cache files:
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python

### Generated Files ###
## Generated LaTeX files (these are generated from YAML data):
generated/

## Build artifacts
*.aux
*.log
*.out
*.fdb_latexmk
*.fls
*.synctex.gz

## Note: The output/ directory contains generated PDFs which may or may not be tracked

### Private generation archives ###
## Raw job-specific generation runs belong in a private companion repo.
.archive/
archives/private/
custom-generations/
runs/

### Plugin packaging residue ###
## The repo-local document-generator plugin is tracked here. Nested checkout
## metadata from the separate packaging repo should never be committed.
plugins/document-generator/.git/
plugins/document-generator/.gitignore

### Claude Code per-user overrides ###
## .claude/settings.json is tracked; per-user overrides stay local.
.claude/settings.local.json
